@NODE OperationNotes "Operation Notes"
@TOC Main
@{LINDENT 1}

@{b}Operation Notes@{ub}



Press the Help key for AmigaGuide help.


It can be started in WBStartup and iconified so it is always available.


The Load Preferences and Save Preferences menus load/save the Project Name,
Project Path, Version Name and Language.


The Load and Save gadgets load/save the version statistics.


If you specify AUTOBUMP, VERSION, DATE, or TIME the user interface will
not be opened.


If you want support for other programming languages, send me several example
files with comments with everything that is included in the C version.


NOTE: The first 10 lines MUST be the same for all languages, except for the
comment types.  Anything afterwards can be changed.


